nl.naturalis.nda.domain

Class ScientificName

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.nda.domain.ScientificName

  • public class ScientificName
extends Object
    This class encapsulates a taxon's full scientific name and the components it is composed of. Only the full scientific name will always be set. Individual name components will only be set if they were provided separately by the source system.

      • isSameScientificName

        public boolean isSameScientificName(ScientificName scientificName)
        Check if the given scientific name is the same as this one. An object is equal if the following fields have the same value:
        • genusOrMonomial
        • specificEpithet
        • infraspecificEpithet
        Parameters:
        scientificName - the scientificName to check
        Returns:
        true if fields have the same value
